{"tid":2435252,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"前排出咗冊，有冇師兄想學鋼琴","createTime":"2021-03-06T06:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T08:51:49.000Z","uid":373174,"like":282,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"19294889eb40f0b712b1f023997c45c830da31c7","tid":2435252,"uid":373174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"入去前都開過po話幫啲手足義教鋼琴/收平啲，之後教教下就入咗去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好對唔住佢哋<br />\n<br />\n小弟雖然只有一年教學經驗，但會好用心教，主要教classical ，流行音樂姐係彈chord仲學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但有琴譜我就教到。一開始會教視譜、音符、音名等等嘅樂理，之後再試下彈啲歌仔咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果有師兄係上緊庭/有經濟困難可以好平咁教，就算師兄唔係想學琴，有咩關於學琴既野都可以tg 問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/shrimpanddino\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshrimpanddino&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b3e66ede\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shrimpanddino</a>"},{"pid":"0c1311c58fb88cd2f764f92b70d7cc72deabbaa4","tid":2435252,"uid":373174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff30a875b531c54d9a1354159ca44646998227ec","tid":2435252,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"特種兵無意見"},{"pid":"8e1e3a3092e218dafe92eaca4d2b37b8877cde08","tid":2435252,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebe26852332fa1f3763d9994f2dfeb3df55737b0","tid":2435252,"uid":349220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbfeb007c25fe51e3fde37a6abb7db22f7eae71","tid":2435252,"uid":223428,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"默默幫你推。<br /