ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"成人 學緊琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"946652218620e5bdf9bde172525683c8c39b0dd9","tid":2435252,"uid":30364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"我都初學 幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eae2ed8011d6e1309992434923384ea42cefc3","tid":2435252,"uid":194899,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"deae08c090db44aed667f10ed44558a7d83849a1","tid":2435252,"uid":233118,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"學琴感覺要細細個學<br />\n大個咗學會唔會辛苦啲<br />\n利申細個冇學樂器 有啲後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"師兄你可以試下睇一本書叫刻意練習<br />\n果位出書人係專門研究人類習慣嘅研究者<br />\n佢左好長時間嘅紀錄實驗，證明左就算大個咗都可以成功練到好多唔同嘅嘢，包括鋼琴小提琴等等<br />\n當然細細個開始練係好嘅，但大個之後練個腦部嘅發展都可以有所改變，好多時同細細個練嘅人分別甚至唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好限死自己覺得冇可能，依個就係人類突破唔到極限嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：26歲睇完之後走去學琴，依家練左2個月已經練到可以慢慢彈到好多歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df6815962352339705db961cdf979499ece18ef","tid":2435252,"uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f6b7b53d70489abeff84f01d4f80a03e28b97c","tid":2435252,"uid":373174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5870a26e2009125d0ed56d68a2f02a372f186e4f","tid":2435252,"uid":194420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19294889eb40f0b712b1f023997c45c830da31c7","tid":2435252,"uid":373174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"入去前都開過po話幫啲手足義教鋼琴/收平啲，之後教教下就入咗去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好對唔住佢哋<br />\n<br />\n小弟雖然只有一年教學經驗，但會好用心教，主要教classical ，流行音樂姐係彈chord仲學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但有琴譜我就教到。一開始會教視譜、音符、音名等等嘅樂理，之後再試下彈啲歌仔咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果有師兄係上緊庭/有經濟困難可以好平咁教，就算師兄唔係想學琴，有咩關於學琴既野都可以tg 問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTg:<a href=\"https://t.me/shrimpanddino\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshrimpanddino&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b3e66ede\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shrimpanddino</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"師兄，你有冇話想教乜嘢級別? 可以幫手問問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"Prefer初級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"初級即係起到幾多級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7475042f099b63887b5e9e28896512a9cf19ad","tid":2435252,"uid":373174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5df6815962352339705db961cdf979499ece18ef","tid":2435252,"uid":156133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f6b7b53d70489abeff84f01d4f80a03e28b97c","tid":2435252,"uid":373174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5870a26e2009125d0ed56d68a2f02a372f186e4f","tid":2435252,"uid":194420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"師兄，你有冇話想教乜嘢級別? 可以幫手問問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"Prefer初級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"初級即係起到幾多級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T12:12:33.000Z","msg":"初學-3級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk